<br>
Paying people who are only supposed to go over bills passed in congress and the senate  looking for gramatical errors to addwords like &quot;work for hire&quot; in to the legislation just before it's voted on is also a good, honest, and an all american method of having legislation favorable to your special interests passed.<br>
