Yeah, the RIAA is the utter embodiment of virtue, and the scumbag music pirates, (60 million of which alone are in the U.S.) need to get fined several hundred thousand dollars for one song, and be jailed with a FELONY conviction ( via new legislation in the works ) and spend up to 7 years in prison...<br>
